$ Excel: Data -> Data Tools -> Manage Data Model

{ Enable the Data Analysis add-ins

  In order to use → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Power-Pivot, the respective → Microsoft/Office/add-in[add-in] must be activated which can be done with the following message box which pops up if the add-in hasn't been activated:
  gh|about-Excel|/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Data/Data-Tools/Manage-Data-Model.png||

  After activating the add-in, Excel's → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon[Ribbon] is extended with → Microsoft/Office/Excel/GUI/Ribbon/tabs/Power-Pivot[Power Pivot] tab.

}

sa:
  → Microsoft/Office/Excel/data/model
